title: Nihilism vs. Lauren Southern vs. Nihilism.
description: What we're trying to overcome here is not any particular faith, but the desire to have faith: nihilism is not based on a critique of god, but a critique of belief itself.  And, meanwhile, "5 Cures For Nihilism" is a video that proposes that Catholicism could be preferable to nihilism… if that's "the cure" I'd prefer to advocate for the disease.  I doubt that Lauren Southern herself would get much out of this video, but if you're interested in nihilism generally, or in how it fits into my own psychology particularly, this video may have a few interesting reflections to offer.
